| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0870 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d2657ba5-8335-5ee5-9aec-3a51c3ee2f82"
